{"tid":707784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女權撚 請問我打機關你撚事？","createTime":"2018-06-19T01:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T12:05:47.000Z","uid":87892,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"deba0124901b519632233a2d09b687078b5906a7","tid":707784,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"女權撚真係世界既癌症來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公司來左個女同事，我地成班男同事講都係食飯出下打機<br />\n條女西曬臉又話打機貶低女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你咩...我地講緊PUBG咋啵邊度貶低女人呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻Game條女性感你又話過分性感貶低你地價值<br />\n平凡樣唔突出你又話人地唔重視女性<br />\n個角色樣衰又話人地醜化女性<br />\n<br />\n多男人又話女性唔重視<br />\n多女人果陣又話唔專重<br />\n<br />\n無撚病呀你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做野果陣就識得講女人唔應該做粗重野<br />\nDoc既野又唔撚見你跟，日日鳩坐Office扮工<br />\n擺個西格出來同班人講男人幫女人做野應份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家鳩陣全世界圍撚住你轉呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同個毒撚朋友講起佢Twitter之前比班日本女權撚批鬥<br />\n我心諗左乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n之後Send左呢堆野比我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/090824_bbb4263945d4c0fdd8c5eafbe86f0f41.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F090824_bbb4263945d4c0fdd8c5eafbe86f0f41.JPG&h=f1822642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/090829_1b9eb5ce65413e8be579075f7efe1ae5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F090829_1b9eb5ce65413e8be579075f7efe1ae5.JPG&h=430b267f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/090843_02bbd05e0cf5d4e0ea8ff881f43a20f4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F090843_02bbd05e0cf5d4e0ea8ff881f43a20f4.JPG&h=538bbede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係無自覺自己係借女權來方便自己既<br />\n就唔會咁撚大反應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女權唔係問題，問題係撚呀<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed98a56557db55d210c604039d49d2a901cd4aa","tid":707784,"uid":135182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:16:37.000Z","msg":"你拎埋佢份糧都應份"},{"pid":"879afbc7d5e33b270d8549b66ab0cdae097dbf41","tid":707784,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a23ba3c4e60aef78cc8eab39d7aa021c3f3fecc","tid":707784,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed98a56557db55d210c604039d49d2a901cd4aa","tid":707784,"uid":135182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:16:37.000Z","msg":"你拎埋佢份糧都應份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:21:13.000Z","msg":"我都想呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOT我地做<br />\n條八婆就日日準時走<br />\n有時候真係好撚懷疑自己係咪同佢同一個職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4822e79994ae98d72b673d008e76653a870acded","tid":707784,"uid":87892,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"879afbc7d5e33b270d8549b66ab0cdae097dbf41","tid":707784,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"